metadata.name: SYNTHETIC BODY
metadata.description:
It's not 3D, it's a photo with complex neon lighting.
Size of the downloaded original: 
5740x3452 px at 300 dpi
Shot with a Sony NEX-5 in 2017

To create the effect of an artificial female body,
I programmatically removed the nipples and genitals.

SYNTHETIC BODY is the first of a series of cyber photos that I will create and add here. Stay tuned.
